# Kolob, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Kolob () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kolobsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Kolob is located 33&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tlyanada is the nearest rural locality.
